<view class="page safe-bottom"><view class="greeting">北京，慢慢走</view><view class="hero"><view class="eyebrow">BEIJING · SLOW TRAVEL</view><view class="hero-title">把时间还给风景<br/>也还给自己</view><view class="search" bindtap="onSearch"><view class="search-icon"></view><text>搜索景点、攻略或关键词</text></view></view><view class="section-gap"><section-title title="去哪里走走" subtitle="按兴趣探索北京"></section-title><view class="category-grid"><view wx:for="{{categories}}" wx:key="id" class="category" style="background:{{item.color}}" data-id="{{item.id}}" bindtap="onCategory"><text class="emoji">{{item.emoji}}</text><text>{{item.name}}</text></view></view></view><view class="section-gap"><section-title title="趣玩" subtitle="给今天挑一处心动目的地" action-text="全部推荐" bind:actiontap="onAllRecommendations"></section-title><view class="featured-grid"><place-card wx:for="{{funPlaces}}" wx:key="id" place="{{item}}" variant="compact" bind:tap="onPlace"></place-card></view></view><view class="section-gap"><section-title title="行程灵感" subtitle="按自己的停留天数来安排" action-text="查看全部" bind:actiontap="onItineraries"></section-title><scroll-view scroll-x class="itinerary-row"><view wx:for="{{itineraries}}" wx:key="id" class="itinerary-card" data-days="{{item.days}}" bindtap="onItinerary"><view class="itinerary-days">{{item.days}} 天</view><view class="itinerary-title">{{item.title}}</view><view class="itinerary-summary">{{item.summary}}</view></view></scroll-view></view><view wx:if="{{history.length}}" class="section-gap"><section-title title="最近看过"></section-title><place-card wx:for="{{history}}" wx:key="id" place="{{item}}" bind:tap="onPlace"></place-card></view></view>
